Does size matter? Not when the girl that weighs 30 pounds less than you has experience. Sabrina Fox finds out the hard way that being stronger and bigger doesn't necessarily mean a victory at Ultimate Surrender.
Site favorite Amber Rayne is tiny but ferocious. She is 100% intensity; an in your face opponent that never gives you a break.
Amber gets the new girl to submit multiple times to her crushing leg scissors. Toss in a fantastic fingering orgasm during wrestling and you have an Ultimate Surrender.
